                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="summer"></a>Activities for young people during the summer holiday</h3>
                <p>.Croydon's Youth Engagement Team are offering a range of activities to keep children and young people busy during their summer holidays. There are park based activities and projects involving drama, film, music and dance. Download <%= link_to "this leaflet", "/resource/CroydonSummer17.pdf" %> for a host of activities for young people aged 8 to 18, taking place in Croydon this summer.</p>
              </td>
