                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="singing"></a>Soul Symphony Choir Open rehearsal 12th September</h3>
                <p>Soul Symphony Choir raises money for good causes including "Mind" in Croydon. If you want to join the group and help raise money for local causes, Joanne is holding a free ‘open rehearsal’ on Tuesday 12 September at 7.30pm at The Holy Family Church Hall, 115 Limpsfield Road CR2 9LF. Next concert Sunday 23 July 2017, joanne@soulsymphony.co.uk</p>
                <p><%= link_to "Find out more about Soul Symphony Choir", "resource/singing.pdf" %>.</p>
              </td>
